# Copyright Headers

All new source code files MUST include a copyright header at the top of the file, matching the MIT License format.

## Copyright Information

- **Year:** 2025
- **Copyright Holder:** MegaBrain Contributors
- **License:** MIT License (see [LICENSE](../../LICENSE))

## Header Format Requirements

### Required Elements
- Copyright notice with year and holder
- License reference (optional but recommended)

### Optional Elements
- File description/purpose
- Author information
- Creation date

### Placement
- **Java/TypeScript/JavaScript:** Before package/import statements
- **Properties/Config:** At the very top of the file
- **Markdown:** At the top, before any content
- **XML/HTML:** After XML declaration, before root element

